<div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-3">
<p>Storytime is an improv game where a player starts a story with a declarative statement. 
Other players jump in, adding snipets of information until you have a completely fleshed out tale.</p>
    </div>
</div>
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-3">
